## WHAT TO DO IF UNSURE

If a design value from Figma does not map cleanly to a token:
1. Stop
2. Output a comment: `/* TODO: no matching token for [value] — confirm with designer */`
3. Use the closest token as a placeholder
4. Do not invent a new value
